Business Scenario :

Title: Validate Completed Projects and Contact Navigation on Isha Homes Website

Business Objective :

To ensure that a visitor to the Isha Homes website can successfully:
Access the list of Completed Projects
View accurate project listings
Navigate to the Contact Us section without obstruction
Have a smooth user experience without UI blockers (Live Chat)

